#. spoken by Arvith:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1233
msgid "Katklagad!"
msgstr "Katklagad!"

#. [message]: speaker=Guard2_leader
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1246
msgid "Thanks! Irritating little formality, isn’t it?"
msgstr "Danke! Eine dumme, kleine Formalität, nicht wahr?"

#. [message]: speaker=Guard2_leader
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1256
msgid "That’s the wrong password! These aren’t our relief! Get them!"
msgstr ""
"Dies ist das falsche Passwort! Ihr seid nicht unsere Ablösung! Los Männer, "
"schnappt sie euch!"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#. EASY difficulty; Muff Toras corrects Arvith; possibilities for the variables are the passwords listed previously:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1313
msgid ""
"You fool! How could you remember the first password and then forget that I "
"told you that the second one was $second_pwd_name|? Where did you even get "
"$pwd_picked_name from?"
msgstr ""

