msgstr "Ob durch eure Hand, oder die von Tairach. Tot ist tot … (argh)"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1406
msgid "‘Tairach’? Who or what is Tairach?"
msgstr "»Tairach«? Wer oder was ist dieser Tairach?"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1411
